  Maximize sum_i^I C_i X_i (eqn 1a);
  Subject to:
  E_f <= T_f for all f in F (eqn 1b),
  E_f = sum_j^J Y_{fj} Q_{fj} for all f in F (eqn 1c),
  Z_{fj} <= Y_j for all j in J (eqn 1d),
  sum_j^J Z_{fj} * ceil(Q_{fj}) = 1 for all f in F (eqn 1e),
